title: Dave's Friend that is "Sheltering in Place" in San Francisco
description: We talked to Dave's friend that lives in the San Francisco area and is under the "shelter in place" order.  She talks about how it went into affect, what it's like in the city with everyone staying home, and what she's been doing to stay occupied at home.
